[
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">(63:19b)<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03863\" class=\"\">If only</st> you would <st data-num=\"07167\" class=\"\">tear apart</st> the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">come down</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st> would <st data-num=\"02151\" class=\"\">tremble</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> you!</p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">(64:1) As when <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> <st data-num=\"06919\" class=\"\">ignites</st> <st data-num=\"02003\" class=\"\">dry wood</st><p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> makes <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st> <st data-num=\"01158\" class=\"\">boil</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">let your <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">adversaries</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">who</st> you <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">are</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and may the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> <st data-num=\"07264\" class=\"\">shake</st> at your <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">presence</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">When you <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">performed</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">awesome deeds</st> that <st data-num=\"03808 06960\">took</st> us <st data-num=\"03808 06960\">by surprise</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">came down</st>, and the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st> <st data-num=\"02151\" class=\"\">trembled</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> you.</p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Since <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">ancient times</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> one has <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"0238\" class=\"\">perceived</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eye</st> has <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">seen</st> any <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"02108\" class=\"\">besides</st> you,<p class=\"poetry\">who <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">intervenes</st> for those who <st data-num=\"02442\" class=\"\">wait</st> for him.</p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"06293\" class=\"\">assist</st><n id=\"1\" /> those who <st data-num=\"07797\" class=\"\">delight</st> in <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">doing</st> <st data-num=\"06664\" class=\"\">what is right</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">who <st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">observe</st> your <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">commandments</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"07107\" class=\"\">were angry</st> because we <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">violated</st> them <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">continually</st>. <p class=\"poetry\">How then can we be <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">saved</st>?<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">We <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">are</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> like one who is <st data-num=\"02931\" class=\"\">unclean</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> our so-called <st data-num=\"06666\" class=\"\">righteous acts</st> are like a <st data-num=\"05708\" class=\"\">menstrual</st> <st data-num=\"0899\" class=\"\">rag</st> in your sight.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">We <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"05034\" class=\"\">wither</st> like a <st data-num=\"05929\" class=\"\">leaf</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">our <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sins</st> <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">carry</st> us <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">away</st> like the <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">wind</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">No</st> one <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">invokes</st><n id=\"1\" /> your <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"05782\" class=\"\">makes an effort</st><n id=\"2\" /> to <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">take hold</st> of you. <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> you have <st data-num=\"05641 06440 04480\">rejected</st> us<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"04042\" class=\"\">handed</st> us <st data-num=\"03027\">over</st> to our own <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sins</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Yet</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> are our <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0587\" class=\"\">We</st> are the <st data-num=\"02563\" class=\"\">clay</st>, and <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> are our <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">potter</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">we are <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"04639\" class=\"\">product</st> of your <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">labor</st>.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07107\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"05704 03966\">too</st> <st data-num=\"07107\" class=\"\">angry</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">hold</st> our <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sins</st> <st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">against</st> us <st data-num=\"05703\" class=\"\">continually</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Take</st> a <st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">good</st> <st data-num=\"05027\" class=\"\">look at</st> your <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>, at <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of us.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">chosen</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> have <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> a <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st> has <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> a <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03389\">Jerusalem</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> a <st data-num=\"08077\" class=\"\">desolate ruin</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Our <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">holy</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>, our <st data-num=\"08597\" class=\"\">pride and joy</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">place where</st> our <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st> <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">praised</st> you,<p class=\"poetry\">has <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">been</st> <st data-num=\"08316\" class=\"\">burned</st> with <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> our <st data-num=\"04261\" class=\"\">prized possessions</st> have <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">been</st> <st data-num=\"02723\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "64",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">In light of</st> all <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">this</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> how can you still <st data-num=\"0662\" class=\"\">hold back</st>, <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>?<p class=\"poetry\">How can you <st data-num=\"02814\" class=\"\">be silent</st> and <st data-num=\"05704 03966\">continue to</st> <st data-num=\"06031\" class=\"\">humiliate</st> us?</p>",
    "verse": "12"
  }
]